headline: This Stock Is Up 55,000% Since Its IPO: Here's 1 Reason It Could Still Be a Smart Buy
summary: O'Reilly Automotive is one of the top retailers in the auto parts space, where it benefits from durable tailwinds that support steady demand.  In that vein, consider a leading niche retailer that usually flies under the radar.  As of this writing, this retailer's stock is up by more than 55,000% since its initial public offering in April 1993.
